		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I couldn't suit both games in a standard IRQ operation. If I fix Skull &amp; Crossbones, then Hard Drivin' is glitched, and so on.<br /><br />EDIT: it seems they do NOT use a same board..!? <br />S&amp;C requires the IRQ to clock only after reset, next clock ($C001 write).<br />HD' requires the IRQ to clock immediately after reset ($C001 write).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


